## Pipes — Global Registration Only

`ValidationPipe` is registered **globally in `main.ts`** — never per-controller.

```ts
app.useGlobalPipes(
  new ValidationPipe({ whitelist: true, forbidNonWhitelisted: true, transform: true }),
);
```

Request DTOs live in `application/dtos/request/` and use `class-validator`:

```ts
export class PlaceOrderRequestDto {
  @IsUUID()
  customerId: string;

  @IsArray()
  @ArrayMinSize(1)
  @ValidateNested({ each: true })
  @Type(() => OrderItemRequestDto)
  items: OrderItemRequestDto[];
}
```

