## Key Rules Summary

| Concern | Global / Shared | Per Module |
|---|---|---|
| `ValidationPipe` | ✅ `main.ts` | — |
| `GlobalExceptionFilter` | ✅ `CoreModule` (`@lib/core`) | — |
| `SuccessResponseInterceptor` | ✅ `CoreModule` (`@lib/core`) | — |
| `TimingInterceptor` | ✅ `CoreModule` (`@lib/core`) | — |
| JWT / RBAC guards | ✅ `@lib/auth` | — |
| `@CurrentUser`, `@RequireRoles`, etc. | ✅ `@lib/auth` | — |
| Controllers | — | ✅ per module |
| Commands / Queries | — | ✅ per module |
| Request / Response DTOs | — | ✅ per module |
| Feature-specific guards | — | ✅ per module |
| `CqrsModule` import | — | ✅ per module |
| Permission strings | `action:resource` (e.g. `read:roles`) | — |
| Explicit `Promise<T>` return type | — | ✅ every controller method |
| `@ApiAutoResponse*` Swagger decorator | — | ✅ every controller method |
